- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as rank-metric codes have applications in cryptography and error-correction. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper discusses techniques and constructions for constructing codes. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category, but still possible as rank-metric codes have applications in network coding. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the least likely category, but still possible as rank-metric codes have applications in coding theory for distributed storage systems, which can be relevant to machine learning.
